## Aliases

alias zyp="zypper"                          # Shortened zypper

alias zypp="zypper info"                    # Show package information
alias zyps="zypper search"                  # Search package

alias zypu="sudo zypper update"             # Upgrade package
alias zypi="sudo zypper install"               # Install package
alias zypr="sudo zypper remove"                # Remove package
